localmount-ephemeral

A Gentoo linux boot-level initscript to reformat Amazon EC2 ephemeral storage as rieserfs and migrate a number of paths to it.


mysql-init
mysql-pwgen

Helper scripts to configure and secure a MySQL database on EC2.

Runs mysql_install_db if needed and randomizes the MySQL root password.  (Saving the new password to /root/mysql-root.pw for reference.)


